SECTOR-TYPES — All Sector Designations

  Use 'des <sects> <letter>' to change designation.
  Use 'resource *' to find the best sites for each type.

  KEY: Letter — Name (produces / requires)

TERRAIN (cannot be changed):
  .   sea              (impassable by land, navigable by ships)
  ^   mountain         (impassable by all)
  s   sanctuary        (capital, cannot be attacked)

ECONOMIC:
  c   capital          (civilian happiness bonus, money)
  a   agribusiness     (food — needs high fert)
  g   gold mine        (gold dust — needs high gold resource)
  m   iron mine        (iron ore — needs high min resource)
  o   oil field        (oil — needs high ocontent)
  u   uranium mine     (radioactives — needs uran resource)
  j   light manuf      (LCM — consumes iron)
  k   heavy manuf      (HCM — consumes iron)
  r   research lab     (research — consumes lcm, oil, dust)
  t   tech center      (tech — consumes lcm, oil, dust)
  l   library          (education — consumes lcm)
  b   bank             (money — no resource needed)
  n   refinery         (petrol from oil)

MILITARY:
  e   enlistment center (auto-recruits civs to mil each update)
  f   fortress         (defense bonus)
  d   defense plant    (shells)
  i   shell plant      (shells — consumes iron)

INFRASTRUCTURE:
  h   harbor           (ships built/docked here)
  *   airfield         (planes built/based here)
  +   highway          (reduces movement cost)
  w   warehouse        (storage hub)
  -   wasteland        (nothing, can be redesignated)
  p   park             (happiness boost)

